        "TileImage": "$($repository bc7ca5bb-5338-4242-8e65-8562ab521bd6).Image",
        "Description": "Good morning 47,\r\ryour targets are two friends who like to call them self &quot;The Improvers&quot;. Their business, same as today, is to make an unofficial test on human&apos;s body. Today, S. Knox, has been implanted with a device that is tracking every single step and bloodcell in her body. Thanks to Mr. Mack, who is the law side of this business, multiple governments wants to use these implants on every new born child. Our clients are a group of powerful people who want to stop this madness.\r\rGood luck.",
